tika-s0403t9:2_1: Pañcamassa paṭhame dutiye ca natthi vattabbaṁ.
tika-s0403t9:2_2: Tatiye ājānanato aññā, uparimaggapaññā heṭṭhimamaggena ñātapariññāya eva jānanato.
tika-s0403t9:2_3: Tassā pana phalabhāvato maggaphalapaññā taṁsahagatā sammāsaṅkappādayo ca idha “aññā”ti vuttā.
tika-s0403t9:2_6: Adhigatamānenāti appatte pattasaññī, anadhigate adhigatasaññī hutvā adhigataṁ mayāti mānena.
